Song of Solomon 3, Psalm 145, Proverbs 15, 1 Timothy 6


M: GNT Psalm 145:18
He is near to those who call to him, who call to him with sincerity.

C: GNT 1 Timothy 6:11
But you, man of God, avoid all these things. Strive for righteousness, godliness, faith, love, endurance, and gentleness.

P: GNT Proverbs 15:22
Get all the advice you can, and you will succeed; without it you will fail.

W: GNT 1 Timothy 6:10
For the love of money is a source of all kinds of evil. Some have been so eager to have it that they have wandered away from the faith and have broken their hearts with many sorrows.

A: God is always the answer for all of my troubles, i will always call on Him. I will stay near Him
